{"tid":2183227,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[整合][大肚婆］孕婦被黑警主動拉跌多角度鏡頭","createTime":"2020-08-31T21:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T22:06:42.000Z","uid":340729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd8ebcf4ba989283872e73b2fcb6a643a4894dd","tid":2183227,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T21:49:30.000Z","msg":"目前上網似係有三段片<br />\n希望天朝多人見到<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1&mdash;前因</strong><br />\n老公稱<span class=\"red\">懷孕老婆被警撞</span>。　<br />\n夫罵警兼被除口罩。<br />\n拉開距離後<span class=\"red\">雙方口角。</span>　<br />\n警未幾上前拘其老公<blockquote>香港人連儂牆。<br />\n（原本，21:40開始）<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/v=766619437425858&amp;extid=nSv3hJTYOkLd686X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2Fv%3D766619437425858%26extid%3DnSv3hJTYOkLd686X&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7uyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=1daea8c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/v=766619437425858&amp;extid=nSv3hJTYOkLd686X</a> <br />\n（部分）<a href=\"https://streamable.com/rzyzf7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Frzyzf7&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7uyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=fcadb0fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/rzyzf7</a></blockquote><br />\n<strong>2&mdash;過程</strong><br />\n承上，老公後肘被警拉扯，孕婦被另一警拉。<br />\n老公一手簇擁護孕婦，一手示意警方小心，同時，現場其他人士靠近簇擁。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">警突以手肘擒住孕婦後頸</span>，並將重心向警方向推移並拉低孕婦。<br />\n老公及人群為上過程中，多次表示該人為孕婦。<br />\n孕婦最終被拉趺地，老公被多警拉走。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">警噴椒，波及人群及孕婦</span>，最終人群散去。<br />\n<blockquote>（原本未知）<br />\n（部分）<a href=\"https://streamable.com/db3mkd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fdb3mkd&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7uyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=71e88817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/db3mkd</a></blockquote><br />\n<strong>３&mdash;更後</strong><br />\n補充上記者退後後的空白，由５秒開始。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">動武警一行人離開現場</span>，另一男女警上前遞水和問話，孕婦期間呻吟，警在場驅散記者和人肆。<br />\n不久，老公再次現身，慰問老婆並指責警暴，<br />\n<blockquote>（原本未知）<br />\n（部分）<a href=\"https://streamable.com/k26cye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fk26cye&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7uyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=c5e3f8c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/k26cye</a></blockquote><br />\n<strong>４&mdash;醫院相關</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQtFpWw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQtFpWw.jpg&h=caaed70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>５&mdash;訪問</strong><br />\n《立場新聞》記者簡短訪問，語帶悲傷<span class=\"red\">指警察把她推落地</span>，並向她射胡椒噴劑。說罷須由母親拭淚。<br />\n<blockquote>（立場）<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3413059855446277/?vh=e&amp;extid=A48iMzBkw2bkZfJs&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3413059855446277%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DA48iMzBkw2bkZfJs%26d%3Dn&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7uyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=c962fb65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3413059855446277/?vh=e&amp;extid=A48iMzBkw2bkZfJs&amp;d=n</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ef2c6d40f9614194519a01bdf4c17078bd5f2552","tid":2183227,"uid":340729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T21:56:12.000Z","msg":"簡短版：<br />\n黑警撞人老婆，扯人老公口罩。<br />\n人地老公梗發火鬧鬼佢黑警。<br />\n黑警又駁咀，話咩睇住你老婆，用個死人電筒照照照。<br />\n雙方吵多幾句，咁黑警就發脾氣，想拉人老婆老公，但又無人性，竟然一野拉低個大肚婆。<br />\n老公緊係火滾啦，但同時又無力地唔夠三個警察既力，而俾人搬走。<br />\n最後警察就派支水，揾個女警講兩句就算。<br />\n聽講（未ＦＣ），老公仲俾人告返轉頭，咩行為不檢之類。"},{"pid":"6d9327e807ca1513dc5e2054cf835904cda88faa","tid":2183227,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T22:02:42.000Z","msg":"呢個post開錯台<br />\n[整合][大肚婆］孕婦被黑警主動拉跌多角度鏡頭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183232</a>"},{"pid":"c5f8a771166b7efb954953f2ed9d316a9d9d9ce1","tid":2183227,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"